<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>ConnectED - Your Student Networking Directory</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/index.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("./partials/header.ejs") %>
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h2>Your Student Networking Directory</h2>
      <p>Connect with peers, explore opportunities, and collaborate on exciting projects.</p>
      <a class="cta-button" href="/signup">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h3>About ConnectED</h3>
      <p>ConnectED is a vibrant and inclusive online platform designed to bring college students closer together. We believe that fostering connections and collaboration among students can enhance the learning experience and create a thriving college community.</p>
      <p>With ConnectED, you can easily connect with like-minded peers, discover exciting opportunities, and collaborate on projects and initiatives that align with your interests and goals. Whether you're looking to join a study group, explore new clubs and organizations, or attend campus events, ConnectED has you covered.</p>
      <p>Our mission is to empower students to forge meaningful connections, exchange knowledge, and unlock their full potential. Join ConnectED today and unlock a world of possibilities!</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Search and connect with fellow students based on interests and skills</li>
        <li>Join or create study groups, clubs, and project teams</li>
        <li>Explore and RSVP for campus events and activities</li>
        <li>Direct messaging for easy communication and collaboration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions or feedback, please reach out to our team:</p>
      <p>Email: info@connected.com</p>
      <p>Phone: 123-456-7890</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include("./partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>
